      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why im typing this. everything just feels... heavy. like i've spent 5 years building this version of myself around my research and now that the funding is gone and the lab results are a joke, there's nothing left. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting to keep my head above water. i just want everything to stop. i just want some kind of peace that isnt just sleeping for a few hours.",
